ke":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:10:24.000Z","msg":"分咗手兩年 而家仲努力緊<br />\n啱啱分手嘅時候做所有野都諗起佢<br />\n果個sem gpa跌到得2.8<br />\n然後我好努力搵野搞下充實自己<br />\n學畫畫、彈琴、睇書、學潛水<br />\n到而家佢喺我心入面都仲霸佔住好細嘅角落<br />\n但係而經唔係之前果種感覺<br />\n雖然分手真係好痛苦<br />\n但係喺呢段時間學到好多野<br />\n亦更加欣賞同愛自己<br />\n你都得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(不過仲係覺得自己暫時未ready新一段感情)"},{"pid":"81ad84a53ec3a4cab238e6da626eaaba55cec497","tid":1887862,"uid":134095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc528dfe173def0bed7d0d15eac12a6d4dba1b0d","tid":1887862,"uid":17134,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T02:56:23.000Z","msg":"當有另一個人出現，你就會放低到之前果個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b8d24952fd1a9108082c1985f2a38a5d4f9443","tid":1887862,"uid":116684,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:31:27.000Z","msg":"首先, 狠心delete哂D message先, 跟手unfollow哂facebook, ig, 所有social media, quit 哂有佢既group, delete 埋佢個手機number<br />\n諗下佢平時點樣對你唔好, 再諗下自己對佢幾咁好<br />\n出去同friend玩, 發現原來自己冇左佢, 會更開心。"},{"pid":"7264be099c7d556bf7b77f19bd95edb3692bd6ad","tid":1887862,"uid":134095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"17b8d24952fd1a9108082c1985f2a38a5d4f9443","tid":1887862,"uid":116684,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:31:27.000Z","msg":"首先, 狠心delete哂D message先, 跟手unfollow哂facebook, ig, 所有social media, quit 哂有佢既group, delete 埋佢個手機number<br />\n諗下佢平時點樣對你唔好, 再諗下自己對佢幾咁好<br />\n出去同friend玩, 發現原來自己冇左佢, 會更開心。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T05:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ced0cb5e152ecc958b0bfab2b93564d8d02c5a8","tid":1887862,"uid":116684,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7264be099c7d556bf7b77f19bd95edb3692bd6ad","tid":1887862,"uid":134095,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"17b8d24952fd1